        {
            "type": "header",
            "year": "2040",
            "text": "Resource Exhaustion"
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "year": "2040",
            "text": "Although we may discover new reserves of a resource over time, the economic and practical feasibility of extracting the resources will eventually be insurmountable, and—although there will still be an abundance of the element in the Earth's crust—the resource becomes \"exhausted\" in all practical senses."
